Package mumble.nooko3.sdk.NKAuth.NKAuthResultsListener

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NKAuthApiAuthenticateListener
    Interface to use with (Context), and similar, methods, returns the authentication token
    NKAuthApiChangePasswordListener
    Interface to use with NKAuthAsyncTask_ChangePassword, and similar, methods, returns nothing.
    NKAuthApiForgotPasswordListener
    Interface to use with NKAuthAsyncTask_ForgotPassword, and similar, methods, returns nothing.
    NKAuthApiProfileListener
    Interface to use with (Context), and similar, methods, returns the profile associated with the stored token or the given token.
    NKAuthApiRegisterListener
    Interface to use with NKAuthAsyncTask_Register, and similar, methods, returns nothing, to obtain jwt token should call NKAuthAsyncTask_Authenticate
